==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''dicotyledon'''
# any plant in what used to be the ''[[Dicotyledones]]'' (also written ''Dicotyledonae''). Dicotyledons and [[monocotyledon]]s together make up 
''Angiospermae'', the [[flowering plant]]s. Dicotyledons are [[bean]]s, [[buttercup]]s, [[oak]]s, [[sunflower]]s, etc. In the latest taxonomic views dicotyledons are no longer a currently recognised 'good' group.

